{"tid":1886331,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警匪飛車追逐3公里 偷車賊遇上紅燈終落網","createTime":"2020-02-18T23:05:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T00:53:01.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"76f79c074e8ae18191e440dde93eccdd4b6d26fe","tid":1886331,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T23:05:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kYEUsh2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkYEUsh2.jpg&h=8440c524&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n荃灣汀九村附近一個停車場，凌晨2時許，巡警發現一輛可疑密斗貨車，準備上前進行截查，司機見狀心虛，立刻加油開車逃走，警員尾隨追截及通知上鋒增援，雙方飛車追逐約3公里，貨車沿青山公路向荃灣方向行駛，經海安路再轉入海興路，駛至海角街交界時因紅燈停下，司機即棄車逃走，狂奔約100米，至有線電視大廈對開，被趕至警員擒獲拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n警員發現貨車已報失一段時間，車上所掛行車證及車牌不屬於貨車，另外，在車頭駕駛室再發現另一對車牌，據悉，被補男子為慣匪，專門偷車拆走零件售賣，涉嫌偷車帶署拘留調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200219/JNL3PD4IL7E2BKOTPEEQFUDZCQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200219%2FJNL3PD4IL7E2BKOTPEEQFUDZCQ%2F&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDmsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=b58ca7c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200219%2FJNL3PD4IL7E2BKOTPEEQFUDZCQ%2F&h=50d99d5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200219/JNL3PD4IL7E2BKOTPEEQFUDZCQ/</a>"},{"pid":"52c383bff5990965a55075464c8c0f37225a2e3a","tid":1886331,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T23:07:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10c1f16f8f7fcc1f56ab4dbeb276f5818923386a","tid":1886331,"uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T23:13:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">遵守交通規則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1d34af81f76bd3